:{{DIcon|undefined}} Did you want something?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 302020101: Config/Level/Mission/3020201/Act/Act302020101.json-->
::'''Boss Du:''' Lately, I've been working on new flavors for my Flaming Potent Tea. Innovation is the key to business, you know.
::'''Boss Du:''' Check out this new Midnight Cream Tea flavor I just developed. It sounds pretty catchy and tastes great, but its color might look a little unusual with so many ingredients.
::'''Boss Du:''' But of course, boasting about it like this does not a fine tea make. I need feedback and suggestions from my customers.
::'''Boss Du:''' Since you're here, why not try my new Midnight Cream Tea and let me know what you think?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'd love to! ...If it's free.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_302020107-->
:::'''Boss Du:''' Of course it's free. If I can't cover the costs of research, development, and preliminary testing, what kind of business am I running?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Can you guarantee my safety?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_302020109-->
:::'''Boss Du:''' Don't worry. All my ingredients have passed the Realm-Keeping Commission's quality inspection. Plus, I've downed it a few times myself, and I'm still alive and kicking. What could possibly go wrong?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_302020110-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_302020110-->
::'''Boss Du:''' Wait a few moments. Your tea will be ready in no time!
::{{Black Screen|Boss Du pours the Midnight Cream Tea into your teacup.}}
::'''Boss Du:''' Please enjoy!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_302020101-->
