::'''Boss Du:''' I tried to calm you down, but all you muttered was something about the "ultimate truth of the universe" and "the unified theory of maths." At any rate, I didn't understand a word!
::'''Boss Du:''' You were walking unsteadily and stumbling, but now I see that you are safe and sound. I'm glad that nothing terrible happened.
::'''Boss Du:''' ...So, how did you feel about that cup of tea? I'm sincerely sorry if it was a bad tasting experience.
