::'''Boss Du:''' Perhaps that's why you acted weird... Looks like the Flaming Potent Tea was a bit too flaming and potent. I'll have to adjust the recipe.
::'''Boss Du:''' I'll look into it later. Oh, and here's the compensation I promised. I'll give you a call once I've come up with something new.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
